方法详细信息

getName

public String getName()
从接口 AuthenticationHandler 复制的描述
Gets a unique name for this authentication handler within the Spring context that contains it. For implementations that allow setting a unique name, deployers MUST take care to ensure that every handler instance has a unique name.

指定者：
接口 AuthenticationHandler 中的 getName
返回：
Unique name within a Spring context.

setName

public void setName(String name)
Sets the authentication handler name. Authentication handler names SHOULD be unique within an AuthenticationManager, and particular implementations may require uniqueness. Uniqueness is a best practice generally.

参数：
name - Handler name.
